OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOvernight rain clearing away
OL,6,Fthis morning. Then the rest of the day
OL,7,Fwill see some bright or sunny
OL,8,Fintervals and scattered showers,
OL,9,Foccasionally heavy. Showers wintry on
OL,10,Fhigher hills. Colder than of late.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will see showers
OL,13,For longer spells of rain, heavy at
OL,14,Ftimes with snow hills. Clear periods
OL,15,Fovernight with showers mostly dying
OL,16,Fout. A cold night with some frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,176,160,301,260,100,100
