OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FMainly dry with some sunshine
OL,6,Fin the morning, isolated showers along
OL,7,Fthe west coast. Dry but cloudier in
OL,8,Fthe afternoon. Patchy rain and
OL,9,Fstrengthening winds extending
OL,10,Fnortheast in the evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMainly
OL,13,Fdry with sunny intervals and just a
OL,14,Ffew showers on Saturday, these mainly
OL,15,Fin the west. More in the way of
OL,16,Fshowers on Sunday and Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
